<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 04:08:09 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>意大利为远程工作者推出数字游牧签证</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/italy-introduces-digital-nomad-visa-for-remote-workers/articleshow/109210890.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109210890.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;意大利为数字游牧民推出了新签证，使非欧盟远程工作者能够在该国生活和工作。申请人必须具备高技能，年收入 28,000 欧元，拥有大学学位和六个月的相关工作经验。该许可证每年可续签，旨在吸引熟练的专业人员以促进经济发展。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 03:46:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/italy-introduces-digital-nomad-visa-for-remote-workers/articleshow/109210890.cms</guid></item><item><title>总理贾斯汀·特鲁多告诉调查，中国试图干预加拿大选举</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/china-tried-to-meddle-in-canadian-elections-pm-justin-trudeau-tells-inquiry/articleshow/109209945.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109209945.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;总理贾斯汀·特鲁多周三表示，中国试图干预加拿大最近两次选举，但结果没有受到影响，而且北京“不可能”偏爱任何一个政党而不是另一个政党。在对涉嫌外国干预 2019 年和 2021 年加拿大选举进行公开调查的委员会面前，特鲁多在宣誓作证时回答了有关他收到的情报简报的问题，并声称选举是“自由和公平的”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 02:30:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/china-tried-to-meddle-in-canadian-elections-pm-justin-trudeau-tells-inquiry/articleshow/109209945.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国百日咳激增，已造成十几人死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/whooping-cough-is-surging-in-china-with-more-than-a-dozen-deaths/articleshow/109209901.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109209901.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国正在经历百日咳的显着回潮，2024年前两个月的病例数比2023年同期猛增20多倍。国家疾病预防控制总局报告百日咳病例32,380例， 2024 年 1 月和 2 月，该病例数较 2023 年同期的 1,421 例急剧增加。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 02:23:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/whooping-cough-is-surging-in-china-with-more-than-a-dozen-deaths/articleshow/109209901.cms</guid></item><item><title>日本宇航员将成为第一位踏上月球的非美国人</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/japanese-astronaut-to-be-first-non-american-to-set-foot-on-moon/articleshow/109209792.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109209792.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国总统乔·拜登周三宣布，在美国宇航局即将执行的阿尔特弥斯任务中，一名日本宇航员将成为第一位踏上月球的非美国人。拜登在与岸田举行的新闻发布会上表示：“两名日本宇航员将参加未来的美国任务，其中一名将成为第一位登陆月球的非美国人。”</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 02:07:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/japanese-astronaut-to-be-first-non-american-to-set-foot-on-moon/articleshow/109209792.cms</guid></item><item><title>韩国反对派将在议会选举中获得压倒性胜利</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/south-korea-opposition-set-for-landslide-in-parliamentary-election/articleshow/109209337.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109209337.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;出口民意调查显示，韩国反对派在周三的议会选举中有望取得压倒性胜利，这对总统尹锡烈来说是一个重大打击。然而，随着计票工作持续到周四凌晨，为反对派弹劾总统打开大门的绝对多数似乎遥不可及。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 01:10:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/south-korea-opposition-set-for-landslide-in-parliamentary-election/articleshow/109209337.cms</guid></item><item><title>越南房地产大亨因125亿美元欺诈案面临判决</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/vietnam-property-tycoon-faces-verdict-in-12-5-billion-fraud-case/articleshow/109209252.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109209252.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;越南大亨张美兰因挪用西贡商业银行 125 亿美元而面临死刑。在抗议中，兰否认了贿赂、滥用权力和造成经济损失的指控。该审判涉及 86 名被告。</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 00:57:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/vietnam-property-tycoon-faces-verdict-in-12-5-billion-fraud-case/articleshow/109209252.cms</guid></item><item><title>41秒内开了96枪：视频显示美国警察在交通站向一名“不系安全带”的男子开枪</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/96-shots-in-41-secs-video-shows-us-cops-firing-at-man-at-traffic-stop-for-not-wearing-seatbelt/articleshow/109208668.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109208668.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;芝加哥警方在一次涉及德克斯特·里德的交通堵塞中开了近 100 枪，造成一人死亡。警察问责民事办公室发布了视频片段。里德的家人对枪击事件提出质疑，认为里德是一位才华横溢的篮球运动员。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 23:29:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/96-shots-in-41-secs-video-shows-us-cops-firing-at-man-at-traffic-stop-for-not-wearing-seatbelt/articleshow/109208668.cms</guid></item><item><title>FAA 调查波音举报人关于 787 梦想客机缺陷的指控</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/faa-investigates-claims-by-boeing-whistleblower-on-787-dreamliner-flaws/articleshow/109208537.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109208537.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国联邦航空管理局 (FAA) 正在调查波音工程师关于 787 梦想客机机身问题的说法。波音公司否认存在问题，并宣布领导层变动。国会山解决担忧。梦想飞机以燃油效率而闻名，但面临着电池、质量问题以及南卡罗来纳州工厂的问题。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 23:20:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/faa-investigates-claims-by-boeing-whistleblower-on-787-dreamliner-flaws/articleshow/109208537.cms</guid></item><item><title>印度现已成为第四大数字服务出口国</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/india-business/india-now-4th-largest-exporter-of-digitally-delivered-services/articleshow/109208594.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109208594.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 2023 年，印度的数字化服务出口额将达到 2570 亿美元，人工智能的采用将推动创新和创造就业机会。印度在该领域排名全球第四，紧随美国、英国和爱尔兰之后。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 23:24:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/india-business/india-now-4th-largest-exporter-of-digitally-delivered-services/articleshow/109208594.cms</guid></item><item><title>美国将缴获的伊朗武器运往乌克兰</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-sends-seized-iranian-weapons-to-ukraine/articleshow/109181496.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109181496.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国向乌克兰提供了缴获的武器，以援助对抗俄罗斯，但资金受阻。拜登寻求 60B 美元购买武器。在与伊朗关系紧张之际，国际社会仍在继续努力武装基辅。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 04:35:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-sends-seized-iranian-weapons-to-ukraine/articleshow/109181496.cms</guid></item><item><title>伊朗指挥官遭袭后，伊朗和以色列相互发出新威胁</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iran-and-israel-exchange-new-threats-after-strike-on-iranian-commanders/articleshow/109208345.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109208345.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列和伊朗就大马士革袭击相互威胁。随着伊朗誓言进行报复，紧张局势加剧。以色列官员证实参与其中，引发了对局势升级的担忧。哈马斯对加沙的袭击加剧了紧张局势。分析人士警告称，可能会出现更广泛的地区冲突。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 23:07:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iran-and-israel-exchange-new-threats-after-strike-on-iranian-commanders/articleshow/109208345.cms</guid></item><item><title>报告称伊朗正接近拥有核武器</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iran-edging-closer-to-nuclear-weapons-capability-report/articleshow/109208263.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109208263.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 《华盛顿邮报》周三援引官员的话说，伊朗正在接近拥有核武器能力，德黑兰正在迅速积累浓缩铀，“其中一些非常接近武器级别”，他们担心“炸弹可能很快就会出现”。最新事态发展正值西亚紧张局势加剧之际。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 23:02:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iran-edging-closer-to-nuclear-weapons-capability-report/articleshow/109208263.cms</guid></item><item><title>乔·拜登表示，他正在考虑澳大利亚要求撤销对维基解密创始人阿桑奇的起诉</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/joe-biden-says-he-is-considering-australias-request-to-drop-prosecution-of-wikileaks-founder-assange/articleshow/109207790.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109207790.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;拜登总统正在考虑澳大利亚请求停止美国对朱利安·阿桑奇的起诉。阿桑奇在狱中健康状况恶化，以及全球保护新闻权利的呼声在法律斗争中得到强调。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 22:52:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/joe-biden-says-he-is-considering-australias-request-to-drop-prosecution-of-wikileaks-founder-assange/articleshow/109207790.cms</guid></item><item><title>朝中社称，朝鲜领导人金正恩表示现在是为战争做好准备的时候了</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/north-korea-leader-kim-jong-un-says-now-is-time-to-be-ready-for-war-kcna-says/articleshow/109205916.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109205916.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;在地缘政治不稳定的情况下，金正恩强调朝鲜主要军事大学的战备能力。该国加强与俄罗斯的关系，并指责美国和韩国通过战争演习挑起军事紧张局势。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 21:59:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/north-korea-leader-kim-jong-un-says-now-is-time-to-be-ready-for-war-kcna-says/articleshow/109205916.cms</guid></item><item><title>BBC 拆分其在印度的新闻业务以满足监管要求</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/bbc-splits-up-its-news-operation-in-india-to-meet-regulations/articleshow/109204755.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109204755.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; BBC 将其印度新闻业务进行了拆分，前员工创建了集体新闻室以遵守外国直接投资法。印度政府对数字新闻服务实行 26% 的外国直接投资上限。在有争议的莫迪纪录片发布后进行了税务调查。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 18:47:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/bbc-splits-up-its-news-operation-in-india-to-meet-regulations/articleshow/109204755.cms</guid></item><item><title>着眼中国：日本推出二战以来第一艘完整航母</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/eye-on-china-japan-launches-first-full-aircraft-carrier-since-wwii/articleshow/109202607.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109202607.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;日本将加贺号军舰改造为二战以来该国第一艘成熟的航空母舰，在其军事现代化努力中取得了一个值得注意的里程碑。加贺号此前被指定为直升机航母，现已进行了大幅改进，以适应 F-35 闪电 II 隐形战斗机的部署，这标志着日本防御能力在地区紧张局势升级的情况下进入了转型阶段。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 16:06:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/eye-on-china-japan-launches-first-full-aircraft-carrier-since-wwii/articleshow/109202607.cms</guid></item><item><title>“这似乎不对”：美国穆斯林在加沙战争中庆祝开斋节</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/it-doesnt-seem-right-muslim-americans-observe-muted-eid-amid-gaza-war/articleshow/109202471.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109202471.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 15:50:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/it-doesnt-seem-right-muslim-americans-observe-muted-eid-amid-gaza-war/articleshow/109202471.cms</guid></item><item><title>为什么美国立法者希望对中国公民实行严格的签证规定</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-lawmakers-for-strict-visa-rules-to-protect-us-military-secrets-from-chinese-espionage/articleshow/109201689.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109201689.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 15:42:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-lawmakers-for-strict-visa-rules-to-protect-us-military-secrets-from-chinese-espionage/articleshow/109201689.cms</guid></item><item><title>巨大的财富转移：中国如何改变全球黄金市场动态</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/a-great-wealth-transfer-how-china-is-changing-global-gold-market-dynamics/articleshow/109201685.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109201685.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 15:37:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/a-great-wealth-transfer-how-china-is-changing-global-gold-market-dynamics/articleshow/109201685.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦：卡拉奇人民在开斋节庆祝活动中继续面临严重缺水问题</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-people-in-karachi-continue-to-face-acute-water-shortages-amid-eid-ul-fitr-celebrations/articleshow/109201598.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/109201598.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;卡拉奇在开斋节期间面临水资源短缺，影响多个地区。卡拉奇供水和污水处理公司负责管理供应，而居民则求助于替代水源。油轮黑手党利用节日期间的情况影响供水。</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 15:20:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistan-people-in-karachi-continue-to-face-acute-water-shortages-amid-eid-ul-fitr-celebrations/articleshow/109201598.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>